{"tid":2317891,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【有禮物】虛擬旅行解謎遊戲","createTime":"2020-12-09T02:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T04:20:35.000Z","uid":225380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1088173cb266bceef5b010bab7e291f07d7bda3","tid":2317891,"uid":225380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:31:38.000Z","msg":"你已遞上辭職信。<br />\n你花了近18000元，買了一張2021年1月1日由香港出發的單程機票。<br />\n你將會轉四次機，到一個很遠的地方。<br />\n<br />\n你如期出發，抵達第一個轉機城市。你感到很疲倦，隨便找了一間機場附近的酒店休息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSJMbPk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSJMbPk.png&h=56210e4b&s={SIZE}\" />、<br />\n<br />\n休息過後，你返回機場繼續行程。<br />\n第二程機準時起飛，準時降落。你想趁着數小時的轉機時間，到一個當地非常著名的景點。<br />\n在坐的士途中，你隨意拍了一張照片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o76h6LO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo76h6LO.png&h=34955ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再飛了數小時，你好像到了一個不同的世界。<br />\n但這次轉機時間不多，只能再機場附近走走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rtgNKD5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrtgNKD5.png&h=a9929917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐上第四程機，感覺要離香港很遠了。<br />\n飛機在深夜到達，你在機場睡了一會。<br />\n最後一班機延誤，你把握時間到市內遊覽一些景點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hooTFii.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhooTFii.png&h=804584e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n最後一程機降落，你快到終點了。<br />\n你的心情難以形容。沒有寄倉行李的你，直接跑出機場大樓，向著目的地狂奔。<br />\n十五分鐘後，你到達這個地方，看見這張椅子，坐下休息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHUfTDy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHUfTDy.png&h=5bf490a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你這時發現，目的地原來已經很接近。<br />\n你向著北面再走了約180米，到了路的盡頭，到達了一個叫______ _________的地方。<br />\n<br />\n完。<br />\n<br />\n如果你搵到呢個地方，可以send email去 xxx@protonmail.com （xxx為目的地地方名，唔駛空格)，email內容為以上5張相嘅google street view嘅link。<br />\n答啱晒嘅，可以得到一份小禮物，名額一個。"},{"pid":"c34c8535563c36383ae2a59266932f4963a1fdf0","tid":2317891,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtMqwBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtMqwBU.jpg&h=7a7c030f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔得閒玩，google太犀利"},{"pid":"f23d9dac7360bee84e79c101752e141b346e6786","tid":2317891,"uid":274343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"78d8dae994104de3f36c15c5316943424b4cc70b","tid":2317891,"uid":225380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c34c8535563c36383ae2a59266932f4963a1fdf0","tid":2317891,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtMqwBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtMqwBU.jpg&h=7a7c030f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔得閒玩，google太犀利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"好快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71c8675662466c3bf867426f2b3c90dcc820051","tid":2317891,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c34c8535563c36383ae2a59266932f4963a1fdf0","tid":2317891,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtMqwBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtMqwBU.jpg&h=7a7c030f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔得閒玩，google太犀利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:52:36.000Z","msg":"第三張個pare係西班牙文"},{"pid":"37b6fcd8d869365fff4510ac7f24a0e3c7d5c4dd","tid":2317891,"uid":225380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71c8675662466c3bf867426f2b3c90dcc820051","tid":2317891,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c34c8535563c36383ae2a59266932f4963a1fdf0","tid":2317891,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtMqwBU.jpg\